dct_title_s: Asia : agreeable to the most approved maps and charts
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Prime meridians: London and Ferro. "Engraved for Moore's New and complete collection of voyages and travels." Decorative title cartouche includes man on a camel. Historic Maps copy imperfect: margins trimmed, with some loss of text.
dct_publisher_sm: [London : Printed for the proprietors and sold by A. Hogg], 1778.
